verbose_text: Interestingly, inhibition of p38, ERK or Smad3 could block the positive effects of miR-433 agomir on cardiac fibroblasts proliferation and differentiation, as determined by alpha-SMA and EdU staining, and reduce the expression levels of alpha-SMA, Col1a1, and Col3a1.
